posting_body: ['COMING 2021!', 'Hailey Apartments offers spacious and light-filled studio, junior one, one and two bedroom modern apartment homes with beautiful designer finishes.', 'Located just minutes from Union Station and countless shopping, dining and nightlife options, your home at Hailey Apartments provides a peaceful retreat from busy metropolitan life.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 12', 'OR Text', '12', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our leasing team.', 'Interested In This Unit?', 'Use this link for more details:', '<URL>', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 363 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Walk In Closets*', '- 9Ft Ceilings', '- Private Balconies*', '- In-Unit Washer & Dryer', '- Quartz Countertops', '- Undermount Sinks', '- Modern Cabinetry', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Luxury Vinyl Plank Flooring', '* Select Units', 'Community Amenities', '- Bicycle Storage', '- BBQs & Firepit', '- Dog Wash', '- Coworking Space', '- Close to museums', '- Walking distance to Union Station', '- Parks and hiking just minutes away', '- Easy access to transportation', '- Convenient retail nearby', '- Roof Deck', '- Storage Lockers Available', '- Fitness Center', '- Secure Package Room', '- Landscaped Courtyard', '- Conference Room', '- Short walk to restaurants', 'Hailey', '1210 Tacoma Ave S, Tacoma, WA, 98402', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'SmH0u1xMe']
